# PCMC Complaint WhatsApp Automation 🏛️

Automated WhatsApp notification system for Pimpri-Chinchwad Municipal Corporation (PCMC) citizen complaint management.

## Features
- 📝 Google Form → Auto complaint registration
- 📊 Google Sheets → Complaint tracking
- 💬 WhatsApp Auto notifications on status change
- 🔒 Sheet protection for data security
- 📋 History log for all actions

## Flow
Citizen submits form → Complaint ID generated → WhatsApp msg sent → Status update → Auto notification

## Tech Stack
- Google Apps Script
- Google Forms & Sheets
- WappConnect WhatsApp API
- Meta WhatsApp Business API

